---
title: Upgraded Steak and Potatoes with Green Beans Amandine
description: Talk about restaurant-quality meals at home! This stunner of a dinner comes together with seared steak, a decadent herb pan sauce, and a colorful pairing of sweet potatoes and green beans. There’s even a French flair in there with a sprinkling of crunchy slivered almonds, also known as amandine.
